Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in successful payment claims
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for a case to move from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases where initial rejection occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases with subsequent 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
